88
00:11:03,860 --> 00:11:06,639
No. I should change it.

89
00:11:11,620 --> 00:11:14,639
Isn't this too feminine?

90
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:19,899
I think a simple bandage works best for you.

91
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:28,959
So you said you didn't know me this morning at the Aizhe Hotel

92
00:11:28,959 --> 00:11:31,379
because you didn't want to make things difficult for me, right?

93
00:11:33,380 --> 00:11:36,899
How much did he drink to get this drunk?

94
00:11:44,580 --> 00:11:46,419
You!

95
00:11:46,419 --> 00:11:48,420
Don't mess around.

96
00:11:48,420 --> 00:11:50,979
Don't take off your shirt!

97
00:11:50,979 --> 00:11:53,979
Hey! You can't take it off below!

98
00:12:07,380 --> 00:12:11,479
Hey, don't misunderstand my intention.

99
00:12:11,479 --> 00:12:16,060
It's because you saved me before. That's why I...

100
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:18,860
I-I'm taking care of you.

101
00:12:28,540 --> 00:12:30,499
