106
00:13:01,299 --> 00:13:03,979
You don't smell like alcohol.

107
00:13:03,979 --> 00:13:07,759
Since you're apologizing, you should drink this to show your sincerity.

108
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:15,579
Could it be that it was fake alcohol?

109
00:13:18,780 --> 00:13:19,959
S-Since

110
00:13:19,959 --> 00:13:23,339
you saved me, I won't hit you this time.

111
00:13:23,339 --> 00:13:26,419
I'll count to three. You should get up by then.

112
00:13:26,419 --> 00:13:28,333
Three,

113
00:13:30,148 --> 00:13:32,302
two,

114
00:13:33,876 --> 00:13:36,083
one.

115
00:13:51,980 --> 00:13:56,039
Listen, you're the one who's lying on my arm and preventing me from leaving.

116
00:13:56,039 --> 00:13:58,479
You better don't try anything funny.

117
00:13:58,479 --> 00:14:01,699
If not, I'll show you no mercy.

118
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:21,179
Are you already awake?

119
00:15:27,820 --> 00:15:28,680
Take a look at this paragraph.

120
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:31,039
- Morning, Director Fu.
- Morning, Director Fu.

121
00:15:31,039 --> 00:15:33,379
Morning, Director Fu.

122
00:15:34,420 --> 00:15:36,679
- Morning, Director. Fu.
- Morning, Director Fu.

123
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:40,639
- Morning, Director. Fu.
- Morning, Director Fu.

124
00:15:41,580 --> 00:15:45,019
Why did I get myself involved with that woman again?

125
00:15:47,940 --> 00:15:51,159
Director Fu has never been late to work. We couldn't get in touch with him for the entire night.

126
00:15:51,159 --> 00:15:53,290
I'm sure he was kidnapped.

127
00:15:53,290 --> 00:15:55,220
Look.

128
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:57,999
What are you guys doing?

129
00:15:57,999 --> 00:16:01,119
The kidnappers will call us anytime.

130
00:16:01,119 --> 00:16:03,119
- Kidnappers?
- We told you to be quiet.

131
00:16:03,119 --> 00:16:07,559
Director Fu has been kidnapped. Later, the kidnappers might call us to demand a ransom.

132
00:16:09,520 --> 00:16:12,900
- Go, go!
- You pick it.

133
00:16:12,900 --> 00:16:15,720
I can't.

134
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:17,239
Hello?

135
00:16:17,239 --> 00:16:19,399
You dialed the wrong number.

136
00:16:19,399 --> 00:16:22,119
- Director Fu.
- Director Fu.

137
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:34,819
- Whose signature do you need?
- Junior Director Fu's.

138
00:16:34,819 --> 00:16:37,339
- Come here.
- What's wrong, Senior?

139
00:16:39,500 --> 00:16:41,019
Be careful.

140
00:16:41,019 --> 00:16:43,480
Junior Director Fu has already returned safely. What are you worried about?

141
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:46,600
You're new to Fu Group. I've been working here for eight years.

142
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:49,059
He has never skipped our weekly Monday meeting before.

143
00:16:49,059 --> 00:16:50,579
I'm sure something happened to him.

144
00:16:50,579 --> 00:16:52,479
Anyway, we should be cautious.

145
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:55,320
Senior, can you accompany me?

146
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:57,059
Just go alone.

147
00:16:58,140 --> 00:16:59,899
Senior...

148
00:17:04,420 --> 00:17:06,259
Junior Director Fu.

149
00:17:07,900 --> 00:17:10,338
I need your signature for this document.

150
00:17:10,338 --> 00:17:11,899
Please sign here.

151
00:17:21,620 --> 00:17:24,499
What are you doing? You're crushing me.

152
00:17:32,620 --> 00:17:35,139
I'll head out if there's nothing else.

153
00:17:35,139 --> 00:17:38,459
That was scary. Senior was right.

154
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:03,659
Fu Zeyi?

155
00:18:07,940 --> 00:18:10,139
Fu Zeyi?

156
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:30,340
Why did he pay me?

157
00:18:30,340 --> 00:18:32,299
Is he doing it again?

158
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,839
- Hello?
- Fu Zeyi,

159
00:18:47,839 --> 00:18:49,679
what do you mean by leaving your card behind?

160
00:18:49,679 --> 00:18:51,519
I don't mean anything in particular.

161
00:18:51,519 --> 00:18:53,879
You can see it... as your compensation.

162
00:18:53,879 --> 00:18:56,599
Compensation? Why are you compensating me?

163
00:18:56,599 --> 00:18:59,179
Nothing happened between us.

164
00:19:02,760 --> 00:19:04,379
That's right.

165
00:19:04,379 --> 00:19:06,219
Nothing happened between us.

166
00:19:06,219 --> 00:19:08,059
So you're deliberately trying to humiliate me again?

167
00:19:08,059 --> 00:19:11,899
You can think whatever you like. This is how I treat strangers.

168
00:19:23,780 --> 00:19:26,230
[Jian Bufan]

169
00:19:31,580 --> 00:19:33,099
Hello?

170
00:19:33,099 --> 00:19:36,459
Older Sister, hurry and come back! Dad is going to kneel and apologize to Fu Zeyi!

171
00:19:36,459 --> 00:19:38,260
What?

172
00:19:38,799 --> 00:19:41,419
Director Jing, you're finally back! Your cousin can't take it anymore.

173
00:19:41,419 --> 00:19:43,220
- Where are they?
- Upstairs. Let's hurry.

174
00:19:43,220 --> 00:19:44,759
All right.

175
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:47,339
Jian Bufan! Open the door for me!

176
00:19:47,339 --> 00:19:49,140
Dad, just wait a little longer!

177
00:19:49,140 --> 00:19:51,719
Older sister will be here soon!

178
00:19:51,719 --> 00:19:54,679
- Open the door!
- Older sister will be here soon!

179
00:19:54,679 --> 00:19:57,559
I don't believe that I can't make him cancel the debt.

180
00:20:02,260 --> 00:20:05,459
- Older Sister, you're finally back.
- You brat!

181
00:20:05,459 --> 00:20:06,939
How dare you sell me out?

182
00:20:06,939 --> 00:20:09,559
- I-I'll teach you a lesson today!
- Uncle!

183
00:20:09,559 --> 00:20:12,199
- I...
- Uncle!

184
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:17,660
Uncle, please calm down.

185
00:20:17,660 --> 00:20:19,899
There is no secret between us in our family.

186
00:20:19,899 --> 00:20:21,559
Let's talk inside.

187
00:20:21,559 --> 00:20:25,259
Let's go. Let's talk inside. Let's talk inside.

188
00:20:25,259 --> 00:20:27,919
Come.

189
00:20:27,919 --> 00:20:29,979
Have a seat.

190
00:20:34,620 --> 00:20:38,639
Uncle. Say, should we use

191
00:20:38,639 --> 00:20:43,139
Simmental cow leather from the high plateaus in Europe or Shinki-Hikaku shell cordovan from Japan

192
00:20:43,139 --> 00:20:46,039
for the boss's new chair?

193
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:49,859
I think Shinki-Hikaku shell cordovan from Japan.

194
00:20:49,859 --> 00:20:51,359
Cow leather is too ordinary.

195
00:20:51,360 --> 00:20:53,140
This Shell cordovan is special.

196
00:20:53,140 --> 00:20:56,579
As the saying goes, we lick one's boots.

197
00:20:56,579 --> 00:21:00,459
Boots made from shell cordovan are superior and easy to lick.

198
00:21:00,459 --> 00:21:03,779
Have you guys ever heard that licking one's boots is a bad thing?

199
00:21:04,700 --> 00:21:07,559
Uncle, you see,

200
00:21:07,559 --> 00:21:10,360
when you sit on this chair,

201
00:21:10,360 --> 00:21:14,199
you do look and behave like a president.

202
00:21:14,199 --> 00:21:16,599
Even if I were to leave the hotel

203
00:21:16,599 --> 00:21:18,539
and leave it to you one day,

204
00:21:18,539 --> 00:21:21,559
I could be at ease.

205
00:21:21,559 --> 00:21:23,339
Really?

206
00:21:27,259 --> 00:21:30,660
That's enough. I already answered your question.

207
00:21:30,660 --> 00:21:32,979
I'll look for Fu Zeyi right now.

208
00:21:32,979 --> 00:21:34,779
Fu Zeyi?

209
00:21:39,380 --> 00:21:44,239
Uncle, didn't you say that you wouldn't compensate him?

210
00:21:44,239 --> 00:21:46,660
I did a background check on this Fu Zeyi.

211
00:21:46,660 --> 00:21:48,739
He is totally ruthless.

212
00:21:48,739 --> 00:21:50,679
He's a true profiteer.

213
00:21:50,679 --> 00:21:53,199
I do think he's devious enough to send me to prison.

214
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:56,179
However, during the investigation process,

215
00:21:56,179 --> 00:21:59,639
I discovered... a shocking secret.

216
00:21:59,639 --> 00:22:01,879
- A secret?
- What is it?

217
00:22:03,540 --> 00:22:07,259
He was missing for three months

218
00:22:07,259 --> 00:22:09,939
from August to October last year.

219
00:22:09,939 --> 00:22:11,459
- I intend to use this fact...
- Three months?

220
00:22:11,459 --> 00:22:15,139
to blackmail him and ask him to let me off.

221
00:22:15,139 --> 00:22:17,059
What have you found then?

222
00:22:22,060 --> 00:22:24,059
Nothing.

223
00:22:24,059 --> 00:22:26,139
Why were you so excited if you found nothing?

224
00:22:26,139 --> 00:22:29,959
It's precisely because of that fact that I know he's hiding something.

225
00:22:29,959 --> 00:22:31,739
Think about it.

226
00:22:31,739 --> 00:22:34,559
What was he doing and who was he with

227
00:22:34,559 --> 00:22:36,399
during those three months?

228
00:22:43,100 --> 00:22:45,879
Fu Zeyi went missing for three months

229
00:22:45,879 --> 00:22:48,819
during the time he got to know me.

230
00:22:49,800 --> 00:22:52,900
