234
00:23:02,800 --> 00:23:04,999
This means you didn't return home last night.

235
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:08,300
And Fu Zeyi gave you an Amex Centurion Card this morning.

236
00:23:08,300 --> 00:23:10,100
What did you two do last night?

237
00:23:10,100 --> 00:23:13,300
You shouldn't meddle with an adult's affair.

238
00:23:13,300 --> 00:23:15,800
He just seems like a troublesome character.

239
00:23:15,800 --> 00:23:18,719
I just don't want you to be bullied.

240
00:23:18,719 --> 00:23:20,200
Tell me.

241
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:25,600
How can a person change so drastically in just one year?

242
00:23:25,600 --> 00:23:28,100
Maybe...

243
00:23:28,100 --> 00:23:30,839
he was possessed?

244
00:23:30,839 --> 00:23:32,500
Come on, be serious.

245
00:23:32,500 --> 00:23:34,200
Maybe he lost his memories?

246
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:35,500
Right?

247
00:23:35,500 --> 00:23:37,599
That's what I thought, too.

248
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:41,700
I must get to the bottom of this.

249
00:23:41,700 --> 00:23:44,600
No problem. Just leave this to me.

250
00:23:44,600 --> 00:23:46,000
Do you know how to solve this?

251
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:49,600
I'll interrogate him by force.

252
00:23:49,600 --> 00:23:51,700
You mustn't hit him.

253
00:23:51,700 --> 00:23:53,400
It's wrong to resort to violence.

254
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:55,900
Don't worry. I'll vent out your anger on your behalf.

255
00:23:55,900 --> 00:23:57,859
Just wait here, Older Sister.

256
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:05,100
Fu Zeyi.

257
00:24:05,100 --> 00:24:08,100
Fu Zeyi, come out. I know you're inside.

258
00:24:09,500 --> 00:24:11,200
Fu Zeyi.

259
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:13,400
Were you looking for me?

260
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:15,259
Stop!

261
00:24:24,920 --> 00:24:28,379
